{"type":null,"faqId":24765,"title":"如何使用设备找回功能？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.6381944in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.045138888in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在遗忘或丢失荣耀 X2时，设备找回功能能够帮助您定位荣耀 X2当前所处的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.7.11.2.2\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86182\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>您的荣耀 X2需满足以下几个条件才可以使用设备找回功能：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n <a name=\"gen-id1.7.11.2.2.2.1.1\"></a><span>荣耀 X2是开机状态且已连接至互联网;</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n <a name=\"gen-id1.7.11.2.2.3.1.1\"></a><span>已经在荣耀 X2上登录了华为帐号；</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n <a name=\"gen-id1.7.11.2.2.3.2.1\"></a><span>荣耀 X2中“找回”功能已开启。您可以在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; 华为云服务”，开启“平板电脑找回”或“手机找回”功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<a name=\"figd0e2346\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86183\" style=\"width:3.5486112in;height:2.5583334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.7.11.2.3.1.1\"></a><span>在 PC 端登录 www.hicloud.com，进入云服务首页。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.7.11.2.3.2.1\"></a><span>在云服务首页点击“平板电脑找回”，在弹出的对话框中输入云帐户密码即可在网页端管控您的荣耀 X2。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>设备找回功能需要连接网络，定位成功后，在网页上会显示荣耀 X2当前所在的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您还可以远程向荣耀 X2发送警告信息、锁定荣耀 X2、备份数据和清除数据等，以减少不必要的损失。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.7.11.2.6\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86184\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":171,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8765","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1430104343000,"seriesProductName":"GEM-703L","visitedTimes":81,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"平板丢失,找回","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}